.TH MAKEBREAD 1 "February 2026" "makebread 0.3.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
makebread \- a simple bread machine recipe manager
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B makebread
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B makebread
is a PySide6/Qt6 application for managing bread machine recipes.
It supports importing and exporting recipes, timer presets for
various bread machine models, ingredient scaling with baker's
percentages, and printing recipe cards.
.SH OPTIONS
No command-line options. The application launches a graphical interface.
.SH FILES
.TP
.I ~/.local/share/makebread/
User data directory containing the recipe database.
